English: Passive: Every 3rd attack deals 250% critical damage and cleaves enemies in a frontal cone within 400 range.
SChinese: 被动：每第3次攻击造成250%%暴击伤害，并对前方扇形区域400范围内的敌人造成等额物理伤害。

English: Attack counter: %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%/3. On the 3rd hit: 250% crit + AoE cleave.
SChinese: 攻击计数：%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%/3。第3次攻击时：造成250%暴击伤害并分裂。

English: Passive: Each attack cleaves enemies in a frontal cone within 650 range for 30%% physical damage.
SChinese: 被动：每次普通攻击对前方扇形区域650范围内的敌人造成30%%的分裂物理伤害。
